#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/manufacturing/quality_control/quality_alerts.rst:33
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Team`: the quality team that will be notified by the quality "
"alert"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Team`: das Qualitätsteam, das durch den Qualitätsalarm "
